---
title: Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt
description: Rich spices, honey and lemon combine to give chicken an irresistible flavour boost. Perched on a bed of tender
roast veggies and fluffy couscous, then topped with zesty lemon yoghurt, this has something for everyone.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
